```json
[
  {
    "context": "Workspace",
    "bindings": {
      // "shift shift": "file_finder::Toggle",
      "cmd right": ["workspace::ActivatePaneInDirection", "Right"],
      "cmd left": ["workspace::ActivatePaneInDirection", "Left"]
    }
  },
  {
    "context": "Editor",
    "bindings": {
      // "j k": ["workspace::SendKeystrokes", "escape"]
    }
  }
]
```

This makes more sense since you're trying to control workspace-level navigation between panes. Try this version and it should work better!
